snippet.title: Spiders of Mars for the Commodore VIC-20 / Commodore VC-20
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

Spiders of Mars is a Defender clone, just without the radar or that you have to save people.

You play as a giant fly and you have to clear the levels from giant spiders, giant dragonflies, giant moths and giant wasps.
